When materialized, press @bind44 to de-materialize or @bind45 to exit your form.

Press @bind25 for server-wide public chat, @bind26 for server-wide team-chat.

Looking for more players? - Try "Client Toolbox" window -> Global Player Chat.

To get a complete overview of the zones, press @bind30 for a bigger
minimap. If you want to look at the precise landscape, press @bind31.

When being pure light you can use the number keys to select what kind of form
you'd like to materialize into.
